snippet.title: Old Game, Pretty Face #0007: Resident Evil (GC) #05 w/ Amber Heard!
snippet.description:
Eksys is finally here! Now she can hold hands with Amber too. Or maybe she'll hog her all to herself; I guess we'll just have to see.

Welcome to the House of Matiq (last two syllables of 'automatic'). He's Riylo, she's Eksys. WARNING: we say bad words. Kids, go outside and catch another Pidgey.

Please read the F. A. Q. before asking questions; 20+ questions answered: http://riylo-eksys.tumblr.com/post/146695872841/f-a-q

If you want to help the stream, you can donate here. We'll use it to make sure the stream keeps going and gets better. https://www.twitchalerts.com/donate/riylo_

Discord Chat for The House of Matiq:  https://discord.gg/caMPZ

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Riylo_Eksys
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/riylo.eksys

Chat Rules:
1. No strong profanity, no offensive terms, no attempting to get around any chat filters.
2. Excessive caps and emojis are treated with timeouts.
3. This is an English-only channel.
4. No self advertising, no asking for subs or views. You will only get one warning, either verbal or timeout.
5. No shout outs, nothing like that. Read the F. A. Q.
6. Respect all in the video and all in chat. If you don't, you can leave.
